## 3. About the “image” field

In the text content I can see product titles, prices, and links, but not the actual image URLs. [hajarafa](https://hajarafa.com/)
To get the **image** for each item, you would typically either:  

- Inspect each product card’s `<img>` tag in the HTML or  
- Open each `Product URL` and grab the main product image from that page.  

